               <code code="42232-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PRECAUTIONS SECTION"/>
               <title>Precaution</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Folic Acid may obscure pernicious anemia or produce remission while neurologic progress may continue.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20210714"/>
            </section>
